It was mapped using multibeam during the same cruise SE1002, targeting a 35 fathom mark on NOAA navigation chart 81004. Cruises               CoRIS Metadata Record Names SE1002              cred_toad_tff_se1002_2010.txt  Resource Description: Digital video images that are geo-referenced to navigation files.
